removideo
=================

A CLI for all video tasks


[![oclif](https://img.shields.io/badge/cli-oclif-brightgreen.svg)](https://oclif.io)
[![Version](https://img.shields.io/npm/v/removideo.svg)](https://npmjs.org/package/removideo)
