# Usage
<!-- usage -->
```sh-session
$ npm install -g vidgen
$ vidgen COMMAND
running command...
$ vidgen (--version)
vidgen/0.0.4 darwin-x64 node-v24.1.0
$ vidgen --help [COMMAND]
USAGE
  $ vidgen COMMAND
...
```
